examples.en: The holiday was marred by bad weather.
A large scar marred his face.
The surface of the table was badly marred up.
Their wedding was marred by the death of Jenny's mother a week earlier.
A frown marred his handsome features.
The student's theme was marred by a number of egregious errors in spelling.
